descriptionHtml:
This a mod that I thought I lost over a year ago but found it just recently in my old emails. I am uploading it before I was able to fix a few bugs. I am not able to get the time to mod thanks to life's new ventures. The mod itself is mostly complete expect for a few little minor bugs. Feel free to fix or make a mod with this. I only ask that please give credit were credit is due. Thanks.

Hearthfires
